[
  {
    "id": "1",
    "title": "1. Two Sum",
    "difficulty": "Easy",
    "description": "Given an array of integers nums and an integer target, return indices of the two numbers such that they add up to target.\n\nYou may assume that each input would have exactly one solution, and you may not use the same element twice.\n\nYou can return the answer in any order.",
    "examples": "Example 1:\n```\nInput: nums = [2,7,11,15], target = 9\nOutput: [0,1]\nExplanation: Because nums[0] + nums[1] == 9, we return [0, 1].\n```\nExample 2:\n```\nInput: nums = [3,2,4], target = 6\nOutput: [1,2]\n```\nExample 3:\n```\nInput: nums = [3,3], target = 6\nOutput: [0,1]\n ```",
    "constraints": "Constraints:\n\n- 2 <= nums.length <= 104\n- -109 <= nums[i] <= 109\n- -109 <= target <= 109\n- Only one valid answer exists.\n\nFollow-up: Can you come up with an algorithm that is less than O(n2) time complexity?",
    "concept": "用一個字典（`dict`）記錄「已遍歷的數字 → 其索引」。\n\n對每個 `nums[i]`，計算 `remaining = target - nums[i]`：\n- 若 `remaining` 已在字典中 → 找到答案，回傳兩個索引\n- 否則將 `nums[i]` 及其索引存入字典\n\n這樣只需一次遍歷，時間複雜度 O(n)，空間複雜度 O(n)。",
    "puzzle": {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "id": "1_0",
          "code": "prevMap = {}  # val : index",
          "originalIndent": 0
        },
        {
          "id": "1_1",
          "code": "for i, n in enumerate(nums):",
          "originalIndent": 0
        },
        {
          "id": "1_2",
          "code": "diff = target - n",
          "originalIndent": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "1_3",
          "code": "if diff in prevMap:",
          "originalIndent": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "1_4",
          "code": "return [prevMap[diff], i]",
          "originalIndent": 2
        },
        {
          "id": "1_5",
          "code": "prevMap[n] = i",
          "originalIndent": 1
        }
      ],
      "correctOrderIds": [
        "1_0",
        "1_1",
        "1_2",
        "1_3",
        "1_4",
        "1_5"
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "08",
    "title": "659 · Encode and Decode Strings",
    "difficulty": "Unknown",
    "description": "",
    "examples": "",
    "constraints": "",
    "concept": "關鍵問題：如何避免分隔符號與字串內容衝突？\n\n使用「長度前綴法（length-prefix encoding）」：\n\n- **Encode**：對每個字串，先寫入其長度，再加上一個分隔符（如 `#`），最後接字串本身。例如 `\"hello\"` → `\"5#hello\"`。\n- **Decode**：讀取長度數字直到分隔符，然後取出對應長度的子字串，不需擔心字串內容包含任何特殊符號。\n\n這樣任意字串（包含特殊符號）都能正確編解碼。",
    "puzzle": {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "id": "08_0",
          "code": "\"\"\"",
          "originalIndent": 0
        },
        {
          "id": "08_1",
          "code": "@param: strs: a list of strings",
          "originalIndent": 0
        },
        {
          "id": "08_2",
          "code": "@return: encodes a list of strings to a single string.",
          "originalIndent": 0
        },
        {
          "id": "08_3",
          "code": "\"\"\"",
          "originalIndent": 0
        },
        {
          "id": "08_4",
          "code": "res = \"\"",
          "originalIndent": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "08_5",
          "code": "for s in strs:",
          "originalIndent": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "08_6",
          "code": "res += str(len(s)) + \"#\" + s",
          "originalIndent": 2
        },
        {
          "id": "08_7",
          "code": "return res",
          "originalIndent": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "08_8",
          "code": "\"\"\"",
          "originalIndent": 0
