  {
    "id": "49",
    "title": "49. Group Anagrams",
    "difficulty": "Medium",
    "description": "Given an array of strings strs, group the anagrams together. You can return the answer in any order.\n\nAn Anagram is a word or phrase formed by rearranging the letters of a different word or phrase, typically using all the original letters exactly once.",
    "examples": "Example 1:\n```\nInput: strs = [\"eat\",\"tea\",\"tan\",\"ate\",\"nat\",\"bat\"]\nOutput: [[\"bat\"],[\"nat\",\"tan\"],[\"ate\",\"eat\",\"tea\"]]\n```\nExample 2:\n```\nInput: strs = [\"\"]\nOutput: [[\"\"]]\n```\nExample 3:\n```\nInput: strs = [\"a\"]\nOutput: [[\"a\"]]\n ```",
    "constraints": "Constraints:\n\n- 1 <= strs.length <= 104\n- 0 <= strs[i].length <= 100\n- strs[i] consists of lowercase English letters.",
    "concept": "**方法一：排序作為 key**\n\n將每個字串排序後得到的字串當作 key，相同 key 的字串即為同一組 Anagram。\n時間複雜度：O(n · k log k)，k 為最長字串長度。\n\n**方法二：字母計數作為 key**\n\n用一個大小為 26 的字母計數元組（tuple）作為 key，不需排序。\n時間複雜度：O(n · k)，更快。",
    "puzzle": {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "id": "49_0",
          "code": "# 方法一：排序",
          "originalIndent": 0
        },
        {
          "id": "49_1",
          "code": "res = defaultdict(list)",
          "originalIndent": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "49_2",
          "code": "for s in strs:",
          "originalIndent": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "49_3",
          "code": "sorted_s = \"\".join(sorted(s))",
          "originalIndent": 2
        },
        {
          "id": "49_4",
          "code": "res[sorted_s].append(s)",
          "originalIndent": 2
        },
        {
          "id": "49_5",
          "code": "return list(res.values())",
          "originalIndent": 1
        }
      ],
      "correctOrderIds": [
        "49_0",
        "49_1",
        "49_2",
        "49_3",
        "49_4",
        "49_5"
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "128",
    "title": "128. Longest Consecutive Sequence",
    "difficulty": "Medium",
    "description": "Given an unsorted array of integers nums, return the length of the longest consecutive elements sequence.\n\nYou must write an algorithm that runs in O(n) time.",
    "examples": "Example 1:\n```\nInput: nums = [100,4,200,1,3,2]\nOutput: 4\nExplanation: The longest consecutive elements sequence is [1, 2, 3, 4]. Therefore its length is 4.\n```\nExample 2:\n```\nInput: nums = [0,3,7,2,5,8,4,6,0,1]\nOutput: 9\n ```",
    "constraints": "Constraints:\n\n- 0 <= nums.length <= 10<sup>5</sup>\n- -10<sup>9</sup> <= nums[i] <= 10<sup>9</sup>",
    "concept": "將所有數字放入集合（`set`）（O(1) 查詢）。\n\n遍歷每個數字 `n`，只有當 `n - 1` **不在** set 中時，才以 `n` 作為連續序列的起點開始往上計數（避免重複計算）。\n\n從起點持續累加直到下一個數字不在 set 中，記錄最大長度。\n\n整體時間複雜度：O(n)（每個元素最多被查詢幾次，且每個序列只會被遍歷一次）。",
    "puzzle": {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "id": "128_0",
          "code": "numSet = set(nums)",
          "originalIndent": 0
        },
        {
          "id": "128_1",
          "code": "longest = 0",
          "originalIndent": 0
        },
        {
          "id": "128_2",
          "code": "for n in nums:",
          "originalIndent": 0
        },
        {
          "id": "128_3",
          "code": "# check if its the start of a sequence",
          "originalIndent": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "128_4",
          "code": "if (n - 1) not in numSet:",
          "originalIndent": 1
        },
        {
          "id": "128_5",
          "code": "length = 0",
          "originalIndent": 2
        },
        {
          "id": "128_6",
          "code": "while (n + length) in numSet:",
          "originalIndent": 2
        },
        {
          "id": "128_7",
          "code": "length += 1",
          "originalIndent": 3
        },
        {
          "id": "128_8",
          "code": "longest = max(length, longest)",
          "originalIndent": 2
        },
        {
          "id": "128_9",
          "code": "return longest",
          "originalIndent": 0
        }
      ],
      "correctOrderIds": [
        "128_0",
        "128_1",
        "128_2",
        "128_3",
        "128_4",
        "128_5",
        "128_6",
        "128_7",
        "128_8",
        "128_9"
      ]
    }
