    "title": "217. Contains Duplicate",
    "difficulty": "Easy",
    "description": "Given an integer array nums, return true if any value appears at least twice in the array, and return false if every element is distinct.",
    "examples": "Example 1:\n```\nInput: nums = [1,2,3,1]\nOutput: true\n```\nExample 2:\n```\nInput: nums = [1,2,3,4]\nOutput: false\n```\nExample 3:\n```\nInput: nums = [1,1,1,3,3,4,3,2,4,2]\nOutput: true\n ```",
    "constraints": "Constraints:\n\n- 1 <= nums.length <= 105\n- -109 <= nums[i] <= 109",
    "concept": "用一個集合（`set`）記錄已經遍歷過的數字。每次遇到新數字時，先檢查是否已存在 set 中：\n- 若存在 → 代表有重複，直接回傳 `True`\n- 若不存在 → 加入 set，繼續遍歷\n\n時間複雜度：O(n)，空間複雜度：O(n)。",
